(55, 1, '2018-05-25 14:37:07', '2018-05-25 14:37:07', 'Originally established back in 2001, we have proudly grown our roots from Eastern Europe. Over the years, we have incubated a number of IT companies, delivered hundreds of <a href=\"/engineering/#engineering-about\">IT projects</a>, provided <a href=\"/education/#education-about\">training</a> to thousands of professionals, and brought <a href=\"/publishing/#publishing-about\">millions of books</a> to the Eastern-European market.', 'About', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'about', '', '', '2018-06-10 20:03:11', '2018-06-10 20:03:11', '', 0, 'http://khiit.loc/?post_type=fullpage_section&#038;p=55', 0, 'our-story', '', 0),
